Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.28,0:22:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天呐 你知道 今天是我的...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}God. You know, today would've been my--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.49,0:22:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当然知道了 不然你觉得我为什么会来?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Of course I know. Why do you think I'm here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.50,0:23:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐们 我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mate, I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.75,0:23:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我很抱歉从你和诺拉的生活中消失了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sorry for disappearing from you, from Nora.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.80,0:23:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.88,0:23:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你这么说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you for saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:13.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天呐 那个男人夺走了我太多东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}God, that man took so much from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.10,0:23:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.47,0:23:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鲁伯特是一个很可怕的人 他建了一座象牙塔把你囚禁在里面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Rupert is a horrible man who built an ivory tower he kept you captive in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.69,0:23:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是你靠自己一步一步从塔里爬了出来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But you climbed every single step of that tower on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.98,0:23:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你不再回到那个家 不再打电话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're the one who stopped coming home, stopped calling.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.61,0:23:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是你让一个六岁的女孩思索 她到底哪里做错了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who made a six-year-old girl wonder what she'd done wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会永远守护你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll always be your biggest defender,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.79,0:23:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你必须承认你做错的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but you have to own up to the part that you played.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.33,0:23:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.54,0:23:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当然是对的 我总是对的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Course I'm right. I'm always right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.12,0:23:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不总是对的 大部分时候你就是个混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're not always right. Most of the time you're an arse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.17,0:23:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这儿呢 该死的 我以为你们抛弃了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There you are. Fucking hell. I thought you guys ditched me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.96,0:23:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-没有 -怎么会!\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-No! -As if!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.51,0:23:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天呐 在此之前我都不知道 我会这么害怕被抛弃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jesus, I didn't know that I had abandonment issues till right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.47,0:23:53.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 瑞贝卡 下一首是你的歌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on, Rebecca. Your song's up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.18,0:23:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-什么? -是啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-What? -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.18,0:23:55.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我没有选歌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, I didn't put a song in.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.72,0:23:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那肯定是别人帮你选好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, then someone else must've done it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.43,0:24:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会是谁呢?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who could've done that?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.85,0:24:03.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞧?你就是个混蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}See? You are an arse.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.19,0:24:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被坏坏的浪漫困住了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Caught in a bad romance
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.82,0:24:09.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊-啊-啊-啊-啊 浪-漫-浪-漫-漫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ra-ra-ah-ah-ah Roma-roma-ma
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.74,0:24:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘎嘎 哦 啦啦！\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gaga, ooh-la-la
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.91,0:24:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要你坏坏的浪漫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Want your bad romance
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.66,0:24:19.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 下一个是谁?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right, who's next?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.75,0:24:21.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Me, me, me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.08,0:24:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,轮到你了 瑞贝卡 上来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your turn, Rebecca. Get on up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.38,0:24:27.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 天呐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you. Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.21,0:24:30.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 我都不知道我要唱什么歌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay. Uh, I don't even know what song I'm singing.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.55,0:24:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我想把这首歌献给我最好的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I would like to dedicate it to the best friend a girl could ever have.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.30,0:24:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我!她说的是我!\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That is me! She's talking about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.02,0:24:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也把这首歌献给我的教女诺拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is also dedicated to my goddaughter, Nora.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.65,0:24:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.40,0:24:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白雪发亮 今夜铺满山上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The snow glows white On the mountain tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.82,0:24:56.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有脚印的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not a footprint to be seen
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.49,0:25:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,孤立的王国很荒凉 我是这里的女皇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A kingdom of isolation And it looks like I'm the queen
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.13,0:25:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,风在呼啸 像心里的风暴一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The wind is howling Like this swirling storm inside
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.09,0:25:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有天知道 我受过的伤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Couldn't keep it in Heaven knows I've tried
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.26,0:25:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别让他们进来看见 做好女孩就像你的从前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't let them in, don't let them see Be the good girl you always have to be
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.10,0:25:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躲藏不让他们看见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Conceal, don't feel Don't let them know
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.28,0:25:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已被发现\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, now they know
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.66,0:25:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随它吧 随它吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let it go, let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.28,0:25:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回头已没有办法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can't hold it back anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.58,0:25:46.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,随它吧 随它吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let it go, let it go
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.21,0:25:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一转身不再牵挂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Turn away and slam the door
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.30,0:25:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不管他们想说的话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't care what they're going to say
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.80,0:26:00.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,任风吹雨打\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let the storm rage on
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.81,0:26:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正冰天雪地我也不怕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The cold never bothered me anyway
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.12,0:26:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-泰德 -爸爸?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-Ted. -Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.66,0:26:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰德？\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ted?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.08,0:26:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,泰德\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ted.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.63,0:26:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.55,0:26:32.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试着呼吸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Try to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.67,0:26:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不行 我不知道这是怎么了 对不起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can't. I don't know what's going on. I'm-- I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.18,0:26:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事了 你惊恐发作了 呼吸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's okay. You're having a panic attack. Just breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.64,0:26:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我疯了吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Am I going crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.89,0:26:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会比其他人更疯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No more than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.27,0:26:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 你没事了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}All right. You're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.61,0:26:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样 很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There we go. There we go. There we go. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.74,0:26:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.87,0:27:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.71,0:27:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想我得先走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think I need to call it a night.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.54,0:27:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要回酒店好好睡一觉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gonna go back to the hotel and just get a good night's rest, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.09,0:27:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,需要我陪你走回去吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Would you like me to walk back with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.88,0:27:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想开我的车吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you want to take my car?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.97,0:27:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 不用了 谢谢你 我很感激\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, no, no. I'm okay. Thank you though. I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.93,0:27:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好吧 -好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-All right. -Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.31,0:27:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 帮我个忙 告诉彼尔德我回酒店了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Hey, do me a favor. Just, uh, let Beard know I went back to the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.69,0:27:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然 你路上小心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Of course. You just get home safely.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.31,0:27:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好的 谢谢你 -好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-Okay, thank you. -All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.44,0:27:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.52,0:28:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-不好意思 醉汉借过 -是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-Excuse me. Very drunk man coming through. -Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.19,0:28:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伙计们 我想我们应该带大家去酒吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Guys. Guys, guys, guys. I think we should take the boys to the pub.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.82,0:29:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我太累了 靓女 抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, I am so done, Sass. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.82,0:29:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我今晚也到此为止了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Think I'm tapping out for the evening too, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.99,0:29:08.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要一个人 带着18个年轻帅气的男人去酒吧?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So I have to take 18 young, handsome men all by myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.16,0:29:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是难为你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, trauma.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.04,0:29:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-好吧 再见 -再见 我爱你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-All right then. See you later. -Bye. I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.50,0:29:15.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朋友们 我找不到我的热带衬衫了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Amigos, I can't find my tropical shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.50,0:29:17.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-他醉得太厉害了 -我们不需要的 你不需要的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-He's so drunk. -You won't need it, you won't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.75,0:29:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 要搭个便车回酒店吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right, want a lift back to the hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.51,0:29:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我想我还是走回去吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, no. Um, I think I'm gonna walk, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.06,0:29:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除非你想跟我一起走 这我倒是可以\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Unless you want me to come with you, 'cause that I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.10,0:29:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-我没事 真的 -是吗?\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-I'm fine. Really. -Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.44,0:29:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且 纪念日已经是昨天了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Besides, that was yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.77,0:29:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-你在浪费宝贵的时间 -是啊 我走了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}-You're wasting valuable time. -Yeah, yeah. I'm going, I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.46,0:30:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我的房间\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, this is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.67,0:30:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我跟瑞贝卡共享一个套房 不过我们的卧室是分开的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm sharing a suite with Rebecca. We've got separate bedrooms though.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.99,0:30:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.84,0:30:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(泰德拉索-谢谢你这么好心 不仅是今晚)
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.72,0:30:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(我们一路走来 你一直如此 这很难得)
